    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading on the clear coat in sun-exposed areas. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few stains, though the cabin remains smoke-free and generally tidy. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, having received regular oil changes, though it may require some minor suspension work or a tune-up in the near future to keep it at its best. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that reflects its mileage and age accurately.",
