    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true collector-grade example that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since new. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, recently enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating; the body is entirely free of rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state\u2014the premium leather bolsters show zero signs of entry wear, the carpets have been protected by original floor mats since day one, and the dashboard is completely free of UV damage or rattles. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete, folder-bound service history documenting every oil change and inspection, including a recent comprehensive fluid flush and a clean bill of health from a specialist. Every electronic component, switch, and driver-assist feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The sale includes both sets of master keys, all original owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
